    <item>
      <title>Smoke Tests</title>
      <link>https://blog.tangly.net/docs/domains/ui/smoketests/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2019 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://blog.tangly.net/docs/domains/ui/smoketests/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;sect1&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;_smoke_tests&#34;&gt;Smoke Tests&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;sectionbody&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;paragraph&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The goal is to test the ERP functionalities in a quick and efficient way.&#xA;The smoke tests are a subset of the test cases that are run on the ERP system to ensure that the most crucial functions of a program work.&#xA;The smoke tests are run to determine if the ERP system is stable and can be used for further testing.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;paragraph&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The tests are:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;olist arabic&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;ol class=&#34;arabic&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Login to the ERP system with the default user&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Load the TSV data for each bounded domain.&#xA;The files contain all data for the tangly llc company since its inception.&#xA;No errors should be displayed in the log trace.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Generate all invoices since 2015-01-01 for the company.&#xA;The invoices are generated with QR code and the EN 16931 embedded information.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Generate efforts reports for marcel baumann on two projects per month for a whole year.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Visualize the analytics graphs defined in the customer domain.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
    </item>
